Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, we're going to start Kaleido Star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star, \Nkeep your room brightly lit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, Miss Layla! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, have you ever been told, \N"Don't push yourself too hard"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"You should try it next time," or{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Why don't you try harder next \Ntime?" or something like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there is something I can't \Naccomplish unless I do it right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to fight now. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to feel regret \Nbecause I didn't try.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want that! I don't want that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dare mo sagashiteru yume wa kitto aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dokoka ni aru {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:01:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Negai ga itsuka kanau made hitori ja nai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saigo made yareru to ittetane {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kitto tsuyogatte itanda {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Itsudatte muchabakka de zutto karamawari de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dakedo anata dake ga soba ni ita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Daremo sagashiteru yume wa kitto aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arukidaseru {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koko kara nanika ga hajimaru {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shinjite itai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mada minu hikari yakusoku \Nno basho e to tsuzuite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Negai ga itsuka kanau made hitori ja naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an amazing appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to eat a lot first if \NI want to gain muscle mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla said she would eat her \Nmeal in her room again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She stopped trying to \Nlose weight, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she wanted \Nto keep her concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll take her meal to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:52.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"An Amazing Bond."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem a little tired, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in Japan, we have something \Nwe call "{\i1}Ume-boshi{\i0}."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}very {\i0}sour, but it \Nworks when you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some specially pickled by my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get some for you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay if I sleep well tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your concern, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be all right by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making me dizzy! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm in a good mood because Miss Layla \Nand I are finally partners for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I think it's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think no matter what the \Nlegendary great maneuver is like,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can definitely pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'm going to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't you think it's about time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about the legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reversed Empress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A suffering queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A suffering queen? It means...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just hit your shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just lost my balance and \Nscratched it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be...? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She really hit her shoulder after all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be. It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she made a promise \Nnot to keep any secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I'm Miss Layla's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the swing, jump across \Nto the log over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then push off that log with your hand \Nand come back to the original swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the final stage of practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late because I was putting this on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, I weigh the same as Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weights used for scuba diving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you bear all the burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're partners, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you still don't have enough \Nskill. But we don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work yourself to death and master it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back to Kaleido Stage tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Match each other's timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's lagging.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's because of those weights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can, like, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me worry about the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put everything you have into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Your timing is getting synchronized.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me try one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Miss Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're matching \Nyour timing to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue. We shouldn't waste time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A little longer... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please last a little longer. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, is something wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:08:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm positive she was holding \Nher right shoulder back then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could she be hiding an injury? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, why? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She promised to tell me \Neverything from now on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why in the world are you \Nwearing something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken said that you looked down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we wondered if you were worrying \Nabout the show the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in your future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think maybe this was a bad idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mia, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I can do is believe. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already made up my mind \Nto believe in Miss Layla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once I've made up my mind like this,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to believe in Miss \NLayla no matter what.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The upright Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lingering doubts and hidden anxieties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really believe in \Nher no matter what, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've returned to Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla and I both \Ndid everything we could.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomorrow, we're going to \Nperform before the audience. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet you still say we're not qualified?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Layla, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here realized that the \Ncurrent Kaleido Stage is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's show...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until it's your time to appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to do our best \Nto heighten the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us be part of a true show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has that so-called spirit \Nof the stage qualified you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just means that you're \Nnot capable after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, I can cancel the \Nperformance with just one phone call,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and finish everything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry them unnecessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you say something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't give a damn about the cast's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time to wake up, Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that you'll be able \Nto do the legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to waste your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:11.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you see that Kalos is deceiving you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's using you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that I'm able to perfect \Nthe legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here wants tomorrow's \Nperformance to succeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All except you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Kalos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to profit from your death,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take over as owner again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like he did to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether you perfect the maneuver or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage will be sold \Nafter tomorrow's show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the investors' idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So no matter what you do, it's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why perfecting the legendary \Ngreat maneuver means nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was proud to be partnered with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't make an unsightly \Nscene in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, we \Nwill do our best tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will never cancel the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is not good. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems what I did a second ago \Nmade my condition much worse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Familiar smell, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}familiar atmosphere... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm at Kaleido Stage again. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone was waiting for us, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for Miss Layla and me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, we're not qualified to perform \Nthe legendary great maneuver yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where Miss Layla is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to start rehearsal, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where she went.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I thought I hadn't \Nseen you in a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do this to yourself \Nand let it get this bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain must be excruciating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you forced yourself to keep \Ntraining after you pulled your muscle,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're suffering from a stress fracture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get you hospitalized immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is the date of the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla, you can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put unnecessary stress on it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your right shoulder will never be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do something about this pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And please don't say anything \Nabout this to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla! Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So don't make an unsightly \Nscene in front of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unsightly scene? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Miss Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sleeping right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is her shoulder hurting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so... That time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she did hit her shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is her condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tomorrow's performance will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I think I have to wait and \Nobserve her condition a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed it at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to kill Layla too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it, Mr. Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! This is a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Sora noticed her condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no way that Kalos \Nmissed it as a coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy knew what was going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he still let Layla do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos would never do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed Layla's shoulder was hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get Kaleido Stage back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I contacted them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos didn't say anything
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because this is a matter I should \Ndecide entirely for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Kalos?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have done the same for Arlon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I saw his practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew how difficult that maneuver was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, I knew how \Ndangerous it was too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlon said that he would make sure to \Nperfect the legendary great maneuver
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to make Kaleido \NStage more successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had faith in those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on the final day of rehearsal,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Are you sure you can do it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one who caused him to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have believed in him \Nto the last, but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to believe in both \NLayla and Sora to the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally broke free from the past, Kalos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah, this is stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fool me with pretty words!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, tomorrow's show is cancelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, I'll never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla, don't you understand that \NI'm saying it's impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, you're injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would be better \Nif we cancel this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, let's get your shoulder \Ncompletely healed first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have another chance at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A month later?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A year later?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years later?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even then, will there \Nstill be a Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me that you won't \Nbe injured at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what will have happened to me by then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about those people who have been \Nlooking forward to seeing the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show already has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear the thought \Nof disappointing someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After my mother passed away, and I \Nwatched my father drown in grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pledged to myself that I \Nwould never make my father sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In spite of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, make sure to finish the movie shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I disappointed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappoint anybody anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you insist on it that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even betting on your own life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, you've changed, to not \Nknow something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do it because I'll receive the \Nbest applause when I perfect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The best applause...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The best applause...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a duel between me and my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll make sure I'll \Nreceive the best applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I back out now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'll ever \Nfeel the same again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why this is the only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how I feel right now, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to receive the best applause,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also challenge fate with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? For Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to attempt \Nthis maneuver. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I've done it right, \Nplease give me a big hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not afraid of dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make sure to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.90,0:22:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is ripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time is ripe. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Layla... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Layla... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Layla... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Layla... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yume... Everyone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's start, Sora. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star, \N"An Amazing Comeback."{\i0}
